OverviewComp._template = "<template tag-name=\"overview-comp\"> <div class=\"zcat-page-wrapper\"> <div class=\"zcat-page-header\"> <h1 class=\"zcat-page-title\">Overview</h1> <p class=\"zcat-page-desc\">An introduction to the ZCAT Design System and its component library.</p> <div class=\"zcat-page-tabs\"> <span class=\"zcat-page-tab active\">Introduction</span> </div> </div> <div class=\"zcat-page-body\"> <div class=\"zcat-page-left\" style=\"max-width:800px;\"> <div class=\"zcat-content-section\"> <h2 class=\"zcat-content-heading\">What is ZCAT?</h2> <p class=\"zcat-content-text\"> ZCAT (Zoho Catalyst) Design System is a comprehensive UI component library built on the sLyte framework. It provides a consistent set of reusable components that follow Zoho's design guidelines, helping teams build applications faster with a unified look and feel. </p> </div> <div class=\"zcat-content-section\"> <h2 class=\"zcat-content-heading\">Key Features</h2> <div class=\"zcat-feature-grid\"> <div class=\"zcat-feature-card\"> <div class=\"zcat-feature-icon\"> <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\"></rect><rect x=\"14\" y=\"3\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\"></rect><rect x=\"3\" y=\"14\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\"></rect><rect x=\"14\" y=\"14\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\"></rect></svg> </div> <h3 class=\"zcat-feature-title\">Component Library</h3> <p class=\"zcat-feature-desc\">Pre-built UI components including buttons, inputs, selects, modals, and more — ready to use out of the box.</p> </div> <div class=\"zcat-feature-card\"> <div class=\"zcat-feature-icon\"> <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M12 1v6m0 6v6m11-7h-6m-6 0H1\"></path></svg> </div> <h3 class=\"zcat-feature-title\">Design Tokens</h3> <p class=\"zcat-feature-desc\">CSS custom properties for colors, typography, spacing, and borders — ensuring consistent theming across your app.</p> </div> <div class=\"zcat-feature-card\"> <div class=\"zcat-feature-icon\"> <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9Z\"></path></svg> </div> <h3 class=\"zcat-feature-title\">Dark Mode</h3> <p class=\"zcat-feature-desc\">Built-in dark mode support with a complete token set. Switch themes seamlessly without changing component code.</p> </div> <div class=\"zcat-feature-card\"> <div class=\"zcat-feature-icon\"> <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M4 14h6v6H4zM14 4h6v6h-6z\"></path><path d=\"M17 17h3m-3 0v3m-7-7H7m0 0V7\"></path></svg> </div> <h3 class=\"zcat-feature-title\">Responsive</h3> <p class=\"zcat-feature-desc\">All components are responsive by default. Layouts adapt gracefully across desktop, tablet, and mobile breakpoints.</p> </div> </div> </div> <div class=\"zcat-content-section\"> <h2 class=\"zcat-content-heading\">Built with sLyte</h2> <p class=\"zcat-content-text\"> ZCAT components are built on <strong>sLyte</strong> — Zoho's lightweight, fast, and memory-efficient client framework. sLyte provides reactive data binding, a component model, routing, and a data layer for building modern web applications. </p> </div> <div class=\"zcat-content-section\"> <h2 class=\"zcat-content-heading\">Typography</h2> <p class=\"zcat-content-text\"> The design system uses <strong>Zoho Puvi</strong> as the primary font family, with <strong>Inter</strong> as a fallback. Code blocks use <strong>Roboto Mono</strong> for a clean monospace reading experience. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </template>";;
